{
    "uid": "meteo-soil",
    "title": "🌤️ Метео и почва — Meteo & Soil",
    "description": "Погодные ряды и профиль влажности/температуры почвы по глубинам",
    "tags": [
        "wheat",
        "iot",
        "meteo",
        "soil"
    ],
    "timezone": "browser",
    "schemaVersion": 39,
    "version": 1,
    "editable": true,
    "graphTooltip": 1,
    "refresh": "",
    "time": {
        "from": "2021-05-01T00:00:00.000Z",
        "to": "2025-09-30T23:59:59.000Z"
    },
    "templating": {
        "list": [
            {
                "name": "field_id",
                "label": "Поле",
                "type": "query",
                "datasource": {
                    "type": "influxdb",
                    "uid": "influxdb"
                },
                "query": "from(bucket: \"wheat_monitoring\")\n  |> range(start: -3y)\n  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == \"weather\")\n  |> group(columns: [\"field_id\", \"field_name\"])\n  |> limit(n: 1)\n  |> group()\n  |> rename(columns: {field_name: \"__text\", field_id: \"__value\"})\n  |> keep(columns: [\"__text\", \"__value\"])",
                "current": {
                    "text": "Поле Северное",
                    "value": "field_01"
                },
                "refresh": 1,
                "includeAll": false,
                "multi": false,
                "sort": 1
            }
        ]
    },
    "panels": [
        {
            "id": 1,
            "type": "text",
            "title": "",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 2,
                "w": 24,
                "x": 0,
                "y": 0
            },
            "options": {
                "mode": "markdown",
                "content": "## 🌤️ Метеоданные и почвенный профиль — поле `${field_id}`\n**Источник:** Open-Meteo Historical API (ERA5-Land)  •  **Период:** 2024-05-01 → 2024-09-30  •  **Шаг:** 1 сутки"
